title: It's great to be able to get them in the USA
review: I had these for the first time while traveling in another country. They are addictive! It's great to be able to get them in the USA. Shipping took quite a while but that only served to make them taste better... two enthusiastic thumbs up! - Cliffp.s. Your experience may vary. There is the possibility that I'm biased simply because they remind me of a great vacation where I ate several boxes of these things! :-)
